name: Enbydiade6
author: Anubi
description:
A
 refined version of a palette I've made back then but never uploaded, 
which results in a mildly desaturated palette, focusing on the yellow to
 purple hues. In comparison with its first version, a red and black 
shade were added, which makes the transition between yellow and purple 
more smoother. Some existing colors were also modified to make them more
 versatile.
